Net-Amazon-AWSSign version 0.01
===============================
A module to sign Amazon AWS requests - works for both SOAP and REST requests.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  MIME::Base64
  Digest::SHA
  URI::Escape


